ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v27.group

Class OML_O35_SPECIMEN

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v27.group.OML_O35_SPECIMEN
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class OML_O35_SPECIMEN
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a OML_O35_SPECIMEN group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: SPM (Specimen)
    • 2: OML_O35_SPECIMEN_OBSERVATION (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 3: OML_O35_SPECIMEN_CONTAINER (a Group object) repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
